        &hr LEFT_CONTROL A  &hr LEFT_ALT LESS_THAN  &hr LEFT_COMMAND GREATER_THAN  &hr LEFT_SHIFT AMPERSAND  &trans    &kp AMPERSAND   &kp SLASH     &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp MINUS
